n proof document had wrong format — had to be rewritten to match expected `## AC N: Title` format.\n42\t\n43\t### Severity Distribution\n44\t\n45\t| Severity | Count | Fixed? |\n46\t|----------|-------|--------|\n47\t| HIGH | 1 | Yes |\n48\t| MEDIUM | 3 | 2 fixed, 1 deferred (package.json stale entries) |\n49\t| LOW | 2 | Deferred (stubs, dead test suites) |\n50\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_011xzm9pEz9psNMnDFFzJSo6","session_id":"819d45f9-7092-4252-80a7-82eddd3933c2","uuid":"b708f2f6-f9f8-49ea-8936-5a41d3f9951c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:22:36.449Z"}
